OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FIsrael and Lebanon agreed to renew
OL,7,Ftheir fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,8,Fmediated by the US in a bid to remove
OL,9,Fa barrier holding back talks with Iran.
OL,11,FThe agreement came as the US House of
OL,12,FRepresentatives voted to pass a
OL,13,Fresolution that would end military
OL,14,Faction in Iran, defying President
OL,15,FDonald Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
