OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780617775
OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FIn a joint statement released after a
OL,7,Ffourth round of US-mediated talks at
OL,8,Fthe State Department, the two sides
OL,9,Fsaid preliminary security zones would
OL,10,Fbe set up inside Lebanon that would be
OL,11,Ffree of Hezbollah militants.
OL,13,FThe statement added that the ceasefire
OL,14,F"is contingent on a complete cessation
OL,15,Fof Hezbollah fire and the evacuation
OL,16,Fof all Hezbollah operatives" from
OL,17,Fareas south of the Litani River.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
