FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780617775
OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FIt was not immediately clear how the
OL,7,Fsecurity zones would be established,
OL,8,Fbut the agreement calls for the
OL,9,FLebanese army to take full control of
OL,10,Fthose areas.
OL,12,FHezbollah is not part of the Israel-
OL,13,FLebanon talks.
OL,15,F"These steps will enable progress
OL,16,Ftowards a comprehensive peace and
OL,17,Fsecurity agreement," the statement
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@TO]
