OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780617775
OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,F"All countries reaffirmed that the
OL,7,Ffuture of the relationship between
OL,8,FIsrael and Lebanon must be decided by
OL,9,Fthe two sovereign governments.
OL,11,F"They rejected any attempt, by any
OL,12,Fstate or non-state actor, to hold
OL,13,FLebanon's future hostage."
OL,15,FThe latter is a reference to Iran,
OL,16,Fwhich supports Hezbollah and has
OL,17,Finsisted that Israeli attacks on
OL,18,FLebanon be halted as part of a
OL,19,Ftentative agreement with the US to end
OL,20,Fthe conflict with Iran.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
