OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FNetanyahu wants to keep the issues
OL,7,Fseparate and is under domestic
OL,8,Fpressure to strike Hezbollah as he
OL,9,Fprepares for elections this fall.
OL,11,FIn a podcast interview released
OL,12,FWednesday, Trump confirmed a report
OL,13,Fthat he had called Netanyahu "crazy"
OL,14,FMonday in a phone conversation
OL,15,Fpeppered with an expletive.
OL,17,FTrump told The New York Post's "Pod
OL,18,FForce One" that he was "a little bit
OL,19,Fperturbed" that Israel's fight with
OL,20,FHezbollah was holding back talks with
OL,21,FIran.
OL,26,@uD@^OUuD@dO]yD@`OUzD@JO]zD@XOU{D@JO]
