OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FStill, Trump said his relationship
OL,7,Fwith Netanyahu was good, and "we've
OL,8,Fworked very well together."
OL,10,FNetanyahu responded on CNBC that he
OL,11,Fand Trump sometimes have "tactical
OL,12,Fdisagreements" but have "common goals"
OL,13,Fand "agree on the main things."
OL,15,F"We always find a way to work out our
OL,16,Fdifferences," the prime minister said.
