OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FIt comes as the US House of
OL,7,FRepresentatives approved a war powers
OL,8,Fresolution that would halt the US
OL,9,Fmilitary action against Iran, defying
OL,10,Fthe president, as a handful of
OL,11,FRepublicans joined with Democrats to
OL,12,Fend the three-month-long war that has
OL,13,Freordered politics at home and abroad.
OL,15,FHouse Speaker Mike Johnson had tried
OL,16,Fto prevent an outcome that would show
OL,17,Fthe mounting opposition to the war,
OL,18,Fabruptly shutting down floor action
OL,19,Ftwo weeks ago when the war powers
OL,20,Fresolution was on the verge of
OL,21,Fapproval.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
