FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780617775
OL,3,CUS says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,Crenew fragile ceasefire after talks
OL,6,FBut displeasure has only grown as the
OL,7,Fconflict drags on and as Trump
OL,8,Fstruggles to negotiate a quick
OL,9,Fresolution.
OL,11,FThe roll call on Wednesday was 215-
OL,12,F208, and cheers erupted in the House
OL,13,Fchamber.
OL,15,F"This reckless and costly war of
OL,16,Fchoice needs to end today," House
OL,17,FDemocratic Leader Hakeem Jeffries of
OL,18,FNew York said earlier in the week.
